insights: - **Tasks**: A dedicated section for tasks, organized by status (To Do, In Progress, Completed).
- **Team**: A section to manage team members and their roles.
- **Reports**: Access to analytics and reports on productivity.
- **Breadcrumb Navigation** at the top (e.g., Dashboard > Project Name > Tasks).
- Description: Retrieve details of a specific book by ID.
- Multiple tabs (Overview, Tasks, Files, Discussion) for detailed insights.
- Action Buttons for adding tasks, uploading files, and starting discussions.
- Task Cards with essential details (Title, Assignee, Due Date, Status, Priority).
- Drag-and-drop functionality in Kanban view for efficient task management.
- Ensure responsive design for mobile and tablet users.
